The paper deals with the problem of influence maximization in social networks, which is a topic that falls under the sub-categories of social and information networks (cs.SI) and social computing (cs.SOC). The paper also proposes a model for maximizing influence based on hyperparameters, which involves machine learning techniques and optimization algorithms, making it relevant to the sub-categories of machine learning (cs.LG), data structures and algorithms (cs.DS), and artificial intelligence (cs.AI).
